        href='https://remix.run'
        >Remix
      </a>. It uses
      <a
        href='https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/Server-sent_events'
        >Server-sent events
      </a> for realtime updates, <a href='https://sqlite.org'>SQLite</a> as database,
      <a href='https://www.prisma.io'>Prisma</a> as ORM and is ready to host on <a
        href='https://fly.io'
        >Fly.io
      </a>. By using Typescript and Prisma on a Remix project, it is made fully
      type-safe from front-end to database. It also uses pnpm and includes a
      heavily optimized <a
        href='https://docs.docker.com/develop/develop-images/build_enhancements/'
        >BuildKit Dockerfile
      </a>. Hence, it is ready to deploy on any container hosting platform.
